imdb.title: The Bus
plot: A Show about Xander and Joseph meeting up on this crazy bus.::Xander Yogert

Joseph goes onto this new bus for him filled with all kinds of unique people. He meets this person named Xander, who would become his friend. They go on to deal with all kinds of the craziness on the bus and become friends with all kinds of people. Noah, Camaro, and Laken all eventually join Xander and Joseph to form the true _The Bus_ (qv) show on Twainzie.
